MAILFORWARD

This program installs or removes mail forwarding addresses.

Synopsis:

$ mailforward { addr(s) | -l } [-r] [-a] [-u username] [-n n1,n2,...]

where:

addr(s)		mail addresses to be installed or removed
-r		the specified address will be removed
-a		if given with option 'r', all addresses will be removed
-l		list all existing forwarding addresses
-u username	perform operation for alternate user (if have permission)
-n		remove forwarding address associated with ordinal numbers

